(BRIP 13066): A colony on PDAB conidiophore 
<normalizedToken originalValue="C–D">C-D</normalizedToken>
conidia. 
<taxonomicName class="Dothideomycetes" family="Pleosporaceae" genus="Curvularia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Curvularia eragrosticola" order="Pleosporales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="eragrosticola">Curvularia eragrosticola</taxonomicName>
(BRIP 12538) E colony on PDAF conidiophore G chlamydosphores H conidia. 
<taxonomicName class="Dothideomycetes" family="Pleosporaceae" genus="Curvularia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Curvularia kenpeggii" order="Pleosporales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="kenpeggii">Curvularia kenpeggii</taxonomicName>
(BRIP 14530) I colony on PDAJ conidiophores and conidium K conidia. 
<taxonomicName class="Dothideomycetes" family="Pleosporaceae" genus="Curvularia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Curvularia lamingtonensis" order="Pleosporales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="lamingtonensis">Curvularia lamingtonensis</taxonomicName>
(BRIP 12259) L colony on PDAM conidiophore O conidia. Scale bars: 1 cm (A, E, I, L); all others - 10 
